messages.messageBody:
Greetings all!

In case you didn't know or have been consumed with the rest of life's busy schedule, here is a friendly reminder telling you that The Early Bird registration opportunity for The Symposium comes to an end in just under two weeks. Normal registration will being August 1st and run through the end of February of next year. So if you want to save a few bucks for Chinese take-out or some gourmet coffee, visit our website and make the Early BIrd Deadline!

http://theautodidactsymposium.com/registration.htm

I'm looking forward to seeing you all there!

Cameron

--
Cameron Lovejoy
Director, The Autodidact Symposium
http://www.theautodidactsymposium.com
